Wheel.mcc/Wheel.mcc

Wheel.mcc is a wheel where you look at the side, it's like the modulation or
pitch bender wheel on a music keyboard.

Wheel.mcc is subclass of Numeric.mui, thus key handling and number conversions
are done by Numeric.mui.

