Wheel.mcc/MUIA_Wheel_EventPri

    NAME
        MUIA_Wheel_EventPri -- [I.G], LONG

    FUNCTION
        priority of the wheel's event handler

        This could become interesting, if you subclass Wheel.mcc to add or suppress some
        event handling. Sometimes Wheel.mcc has to process keys by itself, especially in
        infinit mode. In these cases Wheel.mcc prevents Numeric.mui from parsing the
        keys. To be able to insert your eventhandlers after, before or between wheel's
        and numeric's handlers you can choose a priority for the wheel's event handler
        here.

    NOTES
        Use carefully! Better avoid it

    SEE ALSO
        Wheel.mcc/MUIA_Wheel_Infinit

